text.textblock: On January 25, 1994, a notice entitled ``Determination of Exempt Wholesale Generator Status'' was issued in the above-referenced docket. That notice should have been entitled ``Notice of Application For Determination of Exempt Wholesale Generator Status.'' (59 FR 4912, February 2, 1994).
In addition, the date for comments is being extended from February 14, 1994 to February 21, 1994.
